    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad tn Putna-Ligſdu ug\neij us Zettu/ jeb kahdä Kohla/jeb\nwirs Semmes ar Behrneem / jel\nPauteem / un ta Mahtite pah-\nteem Behrneem / jeb Pauteem\nfehſch:\n"
