    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad tu jaunu Nammu us-\nzehrti / tad buhs tew kahdu pee-\nfleenamu (Lehni) us tawu Juin-\ntu darriht/ ka tu ne kahdu Affina-\nWainu us tawu Nammu krauji/\nka kas no ta nokristu.\n"
